@parthyadav3105 You need to set `OutputFormat` in build options, it is used by buildah's cache mechanism to match against the correct type, following line to fix your issue.

```diff
	buildOpts := define.BuildOptions{
		Output:              "new-test-image",
+		OutputFormat:        "application/vnd.oci.image.manifest.v1+json",
		Layers:              true,
		SignaturePolicyPath: "conf/policy.json",
	}
```

I'm closing this, please feel free to re-open if you see any issues.
